{"tid":2178840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓外長洛欽警告北京若演習波及菲領海　就要作好最壞打算","createTime":"2020-08-28T16:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T17:52:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"443198caabbb529d16f6acef7a32895896da86b0","tid":2178840,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/3f57674f470be50469e1d30ae356f6d4/2020/08/0a2abf99bfe9f9e8dd4ad4edd3bb7d59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F3f57674f470be50469e1d30ae356f6d4%2F2020%2F08%2F0a2abf99bfe9f9e8dd4ad4edd3bb7d59.jpg&h=9f78568a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓外長洛欽接受美國有線新聞網絡訪問，回應報道指解放軍星期三曾向南海發射4枚導彈，指他得知消息後隨即查看地圖，確認解放軍的演習，並非在菲律賓領海座標內進行，但他警告中國如果海上演習波及菲律賓領海，北京就要作好最壞打算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2354743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2354743&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=1e9e1560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2354743</a>"},{"pid":"191df01a83bbdce2fc2d66fa3cbba92dbe6ce6db","tid":2178840,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"中国專家明明講美日台同時開戰<br />\n點解會多左菲律賓架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a62db6004b9f0d0a8fb0055ebdd443bb2079cba","tid":2178840,"uid":14816,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"菲律賓都大聲過你<br />\n叫你要玩就死埋一邊自己玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737c6669713a327a47eb2a68cf661c9b25348d69","tid":2178840,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"美帝借賓佬把口說三道四"},{"pid":"c9c0c7f5cf80f9736bc0f67e7545f63c2e389f7b","tid":2178840,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc